Petal-Tiny version 1.0
======================

Petal::Tiny is a tiny - and thus necessarily incomplete - reimplementation of
Petal. See POD for changes.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

none

